## Expansion Roadmap (When to Add ETH)
```
Add ETH market when:
  1. BTC bot is at "standard" deployment stage (50% bankroll)
  2. BTC bot has run for minimum 12 weeks live
  3. OBI + ROC have been validated on ETH historical data
  4. Combined BTC + ETH exposure stays within max_concurrent_exposure limit
  5. Strategy correlation between BTC and ETH signals confirmed acceptable
```

## Guardrails
- Never scale up bankroll mid-drawdown — wait for recovery to near peak first
- Never retire a strategy during a bad week — require 30-day rolling window of evidence
- Scaling decisions require PM + Risk Quant + QT sign-off — no unilateral moves
- Always run stress tests before increasing total deployed capital
